            <lg xml:id="TK169">
<l>avviya neñcattā ṉākkamuñ cevviyāṉ</l>
<l>kēṭu niṉaikkap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of a man of envious mind and the poverty of the righteous will be pondered.</l>
